{"tid":2046582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國瑜被揭偷步印消費券挽人心  高雄兩萬人演習罷韓","createTime":"2020-06-01T13:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T14:01:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee18fcf6ef5713915736a64267d266e45f190b4","tid":2046582,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200601/AJ25P455RZP5UEF55WFHRBNESQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200601%2FAJ25P455RZP5UEF55WFHRBNESQ%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=d4d7fd77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200601%2FAJ25P455RZP5UEF55WFHRBNESQ%2F&h=4060a2ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200601/AJ25P455RZP5UEF55WFHRBNESQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜被揭偷步印消費券挽人心 <br />\n高雄兩萬人演習罷韓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNWQS4B6ILR3LMVZIYK7G6CBRQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNWQS4B6ILR3LMVZIYK7G6CBRQ.gif&h=57387614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國瑜連日落區視察水患，但避談罷免投票。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n針對高雄市長韓國瑜的罷免投票進入最後倒數，罷韓團體We Care高雄發起「決戰黃金周」活動，遊行隊伍昨拉出100米黃色標語，兩萬人逼爆衞武營國家藝術文化中心戶外空地，高喊「罷免救高雄」宣示決心。昨日神隱不見人的韓國瑜，被踢爆新推出的5,000萬新台幣（下同．約1,280萬港元）振興方案，「今日批出招標合約，今日推出振興方案」，市府更預先印好50元（約12.8港元）消費券。韓被批投票前想透過大撒幣收買人心。<br />\n<br />\n高市府動。。。。。。。。商店已拿到，準備發給市民，韓被批投票前討好市民、收買人心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍高喊「罷韓救高雄」，宣示決心。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OU5QQLC5XPTSAO4TDQ22IUVEIE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOU5QQLC5XPTSAO4TDQ22IUVEIE.gif&h=27ceab88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷韓隊伍拉着巨型標語在市內遊行。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉百米標語遊行<br />\n<br />\n「罷韓四君子」之一。。。。。。。。。。解釋，振興經濟越快越好，才事先印好抵用券，若招標失敗會自行承辦治動。<br />\n<br />\n罷韓投票本周六（6日）舉行，連續第二日上街的We Care高雄，昨早在傳。。。。。。。。。。。選總統，做法不負責任，呼籲高雄人投票罷韓。<br />\n<br />\n比起敵陣密密麻麻的宣傳活動，韓國瑜繼續冷處理，過去多天頻頻落區，處理雨患問題，昨神隱不見人，也缺席高雄市。。。。。。。。。。前再提告。黨團人士分析，罷免投票結果視乎綠營動員與投票日天氣，但評估結果不容樂觀。另外，國民黨籍移民署前署長謝立功，退黨後轉任民眾黨秘書長，過去曾代表國。。。。。。。。。市長均失利，有指加入民眾黨是為再選基隆市長鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n高雄市政府被批評用消費券收買人心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/EhFc-Z3FeOjKMnnLJxOKmahkYAU=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ROS3DWSOVJMQWW5GEVEY4TOH7E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FEhFc-Z3FeOjKMnnLJxOKmahkYAU%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FROS3DWSOVJMQWW5GEVEY4TOH7E.gif&h=a7196f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有家長帶同女兒上街表態。台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"ac9433367ebed5d06487d23e8270be15ef6fa88f","tid":2046582,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc8e3590f7b978da40a65d1d163f00c17caff4","tid":2046582,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"[行動POST]615全民放假悼念日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2046213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2046213</a>"},{"pid":"b718a910687af5359a475df6e26076de8adb51f9","tid":2046582,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47a57ce336c1974942d5e3bce49ce53a4c5a214a","tid":2046582,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"12.8 有無咁易收買到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d406a12a62e525e758c43d8b0e7c86518ea7dbb","tid":2046582,"uid":86246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起反送中演習"},{"pid":"116e0cd81844075b005f4fe16c1b24b23bacef36","tid":2046582,"uid":131696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"錢照收 韓照罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f234d38367ad51dcfa1b141ae6a845d70fae2716","tid":2046582,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"光復高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7aeb9fcdec7bfcb2d3a5ab1077ef2104ea89fb","tid":2046582,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"柒頭奶共仔"},{"pid":"1883360a61c0c7076bd1c98c0cbf8fbc496dafe3","tid":2046582,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"666 非韓不投 有韓必投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}